        "subject": "LDEV-646 lustre-dkms backward compat for lustre-all-dkms",
        "message": "LDEV-646 lustre-dkms backward compat for lustre-all-dkms\n\nTo maintain backward compatibiity, lustre-all-dkms should provide\nbackwards compatibility with previous releases' lustre-dkms capability\nby providing a virtual capability.\n\nThis is needed to not break users of the previou name/capability of\nlustre-dkms.\n\nSigned-off-by: Brian J. Murrell <brian.murrell@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ib62fcb41b0440e03f26c7573c852a39f17503f9f\n"
